  <h1 class="color-match">Careers</h1>
  <p><strong>Want to Start a New Career in eLearning?</strong><br>
  </p>
</header>
	<article class="content wrapper group">
			
  <section style="width:70%; float:left;">
          
            <p>As a <a href="http://www.pearsoned.com/"  rel="ext">Pearson Education</a> company, eCollege is able to offer our  employees a comprehensive  benefits package and the security that comes with our deep connection to  a well-established, global company.</p>
            <p>Because Pearson eCollege is separated geographically from the rest of  Pearson, we have our own  distinct culture and the autonomy to establish  our own structure. Pearson eCollege believes in creating an environment  in which employees not  only succeed but continue to grow. Each  employee is respected as a valuable contributor to our company’s  continued success in eLearning.  </p>
            <p><a href="http://jobs.pearson.com/?utm_source=careersite" class="button forward small" style="margin:0 5px;" rel="ext">View Open Positions</a></p>
      </section>
      <aside style="width:27.5%;" class="float-right"> 
